message.content:
Ndicela ukunikeza iinkcukacha zokukunceda kumsebenzi wakho. Ndizakunceda ngezantsi kumaxesha endithetha ngawo ngolwimi lwesiXhosa. 

1. Ukuthenga ithyala:
   - Hlela ku-intanethi ngekhadi lokuthenga.
   - Faka igama lesikhathi sakho, iindlela ezifunekayo, ukukhetha ukuthenga ngokufanelekayo, nezimvo zokuthengisa.
   - Hlela ngaphambili phambi kokuthenga kwaye ukhetha ikhadi lokuthenga elilungileyo.
   - Faka ulwazi lwakho lwegama, ibhizinisi, iindlela zokunceda abathengi ukukuthengisa, nanye nonyaka wokuthenga.
   - Beka ityala kwi-cart yokuthengisa kwaye qhuba ukunceda ukukhokela.

2. Ukuxhumana nothengi:
   - Hlela ku-intanethi ngekhadi lokuxhumana nothengi.
   - Faka igama lesikhathi sakho, amanani okuqukethweyo, fomula yokuxhumana, nezimvo zokunceda abathengi.
   - Hlela ngaphambili phambi kokuxhumana kwaye ukhetha ikhadi lokuxhumana elilungileyo.
   - Faka ulwazi lwakho lwegama, ibhizinisi, iindlela zokunceda abathengi ukuxhumana, nanye nonyaka wokuxhumana.
   - Beka ityala kwi-cart yokuxhumana kwaye qhuba ukunceda ukukhokela.

3. Ukukhokela ezinkcukachweni:
   - Hlela ku-intanethi ngekhadi lokukhokela ezinkcukachweni.
   - Faka igama lesikhathi sakho, inkcukacha oyikhokelayo, nezimvo zokunceda
